column2: b'Super Real Mahjong: Mahjong Battle Scramble - Konran-teki Sento Mahjong'

b'Sequel of Super Real Mahjong.\n\nMahjong-playing sisters Kasumi, Miki, and Shouko are sent to a world where mahjong tiles are currency. In order to return to their world, they must defeat a mahjong-playing rabbit who rules the land.'
[b'Super Real Mahjong: Kasumi Miki Shouko no Hajimemashite']
